<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: PDA ENGINEERING'S SOFTWARE DIVISION NAMES VP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Thomas C. Curry has been named vice president and general manager for the 
software products division of PDA Engineering, Costa Mesa. 
</P>
<P>
He will be responsible for the division's worldwide operations, including 
product planning, development, manufacturing, marketing, sales, education and 
customer support. 
</P>
<P>
Curry was previously vice president of marketing for McDonnell Douglas Corp.'s 
Manufacturing &amp; Engineering Systems Co. He also has held management 
positions with Auto-Trol Technology Corp. and Air Products &amp; Chemicals Inc. 
</P>
