down in his stable.; Photo, Above, ranch owner Ernest Auerbach. ; Photo, E. A. 
Ranches, a little-known thoroughbred farm near Ramona, focuses on training, 
breeding and boarding racehorses. ; Photo, Trainers Dan Southworth and Sherri 
Songer exercise a pair of horses on a misty early morning. BARBARA MARTIN 
PINHERO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
