LINDA; Photo, This erstwhile "red car" depot is now a restaurant. ; Photo, 
Western Yorba Linda's Richard Nixon Library, scheduled to open in July, is well 
on its way toward completion. HENRY DIROCCO / Photo for The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
