<P>
PALESTINIAN KILLED BY TROOPS IN GAZA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Israeli troops shot a teen-age Palestinian protester to death and wounded 16 in 
the second day of street battles in the occupied Gaza Strip. 
</P>
<P>
Ayman Zakout, 17, was killed during a clash with stone throwers in Rafah, 
