ANGELES COUNTY -- TRANSPORTATION; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- FINANCES; LOS ANGELES 
COUNTY -- TAXES; TRANSIT SYSTEMS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; PROPERTY TAX -- LOS 
ANGELES COUNTY; PROPERTY ASSESSMENT; PETITIONS 
