Circuit Judge Jessica Cooper sentenced Henry Hearns Tuesday in Pontiac, Mich., 
for second-degree murder, said Bill Irving, a research attorney for Cooper. The 
judge also gave him a two-year term for a felony firearms conviction. The 
sentences are to be served consecutively. 
