</P>
<P>
In Spanish: 1 (800) 344-SIDA 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
<P>
Southern California AIDS Hotline: 1 (800) 922-2437 
</P>
<P>
Spanish language hotline: 1 (800) 222-SIDA 
</P>
<P>
Cara A Cara: (213) 660-2400 
</P>
<P>
AIDS Project Los Angeles: (213) 962-1600 
</P>
<P>
